{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"1":"Purification (Kitab Al-Taharah)"},"section_detail":{"1":{"hadithnumber_first":1,"hadithnumber_last":390,"arabicnumber_first":1,"arabicnumber_last":390}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":354,"arabicnumber":354,"text":"حدثنا ابو الوليد الطيالسي، حدثنا همام، عن قتادة، عن الحسن، عن سمرة، قال قال رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم \" من توضا يوم الجمعة فبها ونعمت ومن اغتسل فهو افضل","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan Lighairihi"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":1,"hadith":354}}]}